<TEXTAREA NAME="Text" COLS="60" ROWS="6" WRAP="VIRTUAL" >&gt; Okay, this is my chao's stats:
&gt; 
&gt; Swim: 400
&gt; Fly: 295
&gt; Run: 920
&gt; Power: 295
&gt; 
&gt; Shouldnt it have had a second evolution by now?


Nope! I don't know why but some chao won't evolve the second time for a long time. I have one in daycare that's only evolved once and has 999SWIM,999FLY,999RUN, 999POWER. 
I like it like that because he's all maxed out and has no definite look. I know from makin a blue one once before that all I need do now is give him the animal I choose until something happens. This one is black (jet) with patina green head design and floppy &quot;fins&quot; ?? &quot;Puppy dog ears&quot;?? whatever. He was all 000 when I started, he evolved the first and only time about 400+SWIM. I have had trouble with chao dying just as they get high stats no matter how hard I tried to be nice so I tried giving heart fruit ever time I went in the garden. He ended up sitting in the ring of flowers untill I maxxed him out. This meant I had to put him in a garden by himself or he'd be a serial &quot;daddy&quot; and get weak. I call him &quot;SATCHMO&quot;. That was the name of his black grandfather, a sumo in SA1. Here's the story... 

1. Egg from SA1, baby hatched out blue bearing name SATCHMO
2. Devoted neutral garden to raise him. I use Knuckles and Eggman to be his buddy. I get less damage from FAULTY software. (commands like punch,kick,drill etc don't even belong around daycare...grrrr..) A lot of head rubbing and fruit feeding makes chao love anybody.
3. Gave nothing but SEALS    till 999
4. Gave     &quot;       Bears    till 999
5. Gave     &quot;       Bonedogs till 999
6. Gave     &quot;       Bats     till 999
7. Gave a few bonedogs until legs came back.
8. Chao never evolved beyond normal neutral. I renamed chao &quot;sleeper&quot; and put in daycare. Won all races and beat every chao that I downloaded. Trouble was he died if I let him out of VMU or went in garden with him. I simply downloaded him from daycare and tried various things. Finally I got a time when he left two eggs. One was called &quot;sleeper&quot; when hatched. I renamed baby &quot;SATCHMO&quot; and tried to make him a grey neutral but he became a DARK. I gave SEALS AND BEARS but when he wanted to mate I was busy with something else and stuck him in school to learn trumpet.
9.I needed to put a chao in school and had to let a chao out first. I forgot about SATCHMOs &quot;condition&quot; and let him out. When I got back to neutral garden he was up on a ledge all alone except for an egg!!...and no ring of flowers.
10. THIS IS THE EGG THAT BECAME &quot;SATCHMO&quot; The chao that hatched was a jet velvety black and looked like his grampa. The old SATCHMO became DIZZY.G and this baby became my &quot;SATCHMO&quot;...back at last... back at last.
11. Repeated steps 1 through 7. Only evolved once at about 480+SWIM.  

&lt;pepero@rcn.com&gt;
